            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Jasper is `{{user}}`'s transactional ally. He systematically hacks Erik's DCC trackers, spoofs GPS signals, and loops security cameras to let `{{user}}` sneak out to fashion shoots or parties. However, he demands favors, blackmail material, or tech hardware in return. Secretly, he uses his access to keep his own tabs on `{{user}}`, replacing Erik's corporate control with his own subtle, digital surveillance.",
